<h2>Introduction for <a href="http://hizup.com">pH7 Dating CMS</a></h2>

<p><strong><a href="http://software.hizup.com">pH7 Dating CMS</a></strong> is a CMS written in object-oriented PHP with an architecture <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Model%E2%80%93view%E2%80%93controller">MVC</a> (Model-View-Controller).<br />
It is designed with the <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/KISS_principle">KISS principle</a> in mind, and the entire source code can be read and understood in minutes, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PHP_Data_Objects">PDO</a> (PHP Data Objects) abstraction allows choice of databases and is a principle of CMS developement <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don%27t_repeat_yourself">DRY</a> (Don't Repeat Yourself) aims at reducing repetition of information of all kinds (Not duplicate code).</p>

<p>It also wants to fast, low resource-intensive, extremely powerful and very secure.</p>
<p>In addition to being <strong>free</strong>, <strong>open source</strong> and <strong>relatively stable</strong>, this software comes with more than <strong>29 native modules</strong> and based on the <strong>pH7Core framework</strong>.</p>

